ValidatesAsUri
==============

Proactively validate user-supplied URIs, and DRY up your model code.

Installation:

script/plugin install git://github.com/cmowforth/validates_as_uri.git


Examples
=======

Assuming the database column name is 'uri':

validates_as_uri :uri


